=====Usage notes=====
* The meaning of "née" has become obsolete, as current Chinese practice is for all married spouses to continue to use their birth names. Occasionally, a wife may adopt the husband's surname. As a descriptor, {{lang|zh|氏}} follows the maiden name, which follows the [[married name]] — {{zh-l|[[張]]氏|gloss=née Zhang}}, {{zh-l|[[李]]張氏|gloss=Li née Zhang}}, or {{zh-l|[[配]]張氏|gloss=married to a lady of the Zhang clan}}.

